flowchart TB
    subgraph Fragile Controller
        F0[Nominal model\nparameters]:::base --> F1[High-gain\ncontroller]:::fragile
        F1 --> F2[Good performance\nin nominal case]:::ok
        F3[Small change in\npayload/friction]:::delta --> F1
        F1 --> F4[Unstable or\noscillatory behavior]:::bad
    end

    subgraph Robust Controller
        R0[Approximate model\nparameters]:::base --> R1[Moderate-gain\ncontroller\n+ safety limits]:::robust
        R1 --> R2[Acceptable performance\nin nominal case]:::ok
        R3[Small change in\npayload/friction]:::delta --> R1
        R1 --> R4[Behavior remains\nstable, predictable]:::ok
    end

    classDef base fill:#e7f5ff,stroke:#1c7ed6,color:#000000;
